title: B. Stanley Simmons Architecture - Washington DC
name: B. Stanley Simmons Architecture - Washington DC
description:
Permits for buildings in Washington DC that registered B. Stanley Simmons as Architect. 

B. S. Simmons was a prevalent and well respected architect of DC during the late 18th and early 19th centuries.
